Bootstrap Framework

Aurona is based on Bootstrap Framework, which makes it a nice template for any purpose.

Novi Builder

Use our Novi Builder to customize and update your website within seconds after the template installation.

Responsive & Retina Ready

Aurona looks great on any screen resolution and on any device due to its responsiveness.

Tons of Tools for Real Needs

Event calendar, bookings and schedule are just some tools that come on board with this template.

Multiple layouts

Huge number of content layouts available at zemez.io allows to assemble unique pages with great flexibility.

Clean and Crispy Design

Aurona is crafted by top industry leaders with love, care and customer needs in mind.

Built For Speed

Aurona is built for speed and performance. Get the best results at GTmetrix and Google PageSpeed.

Flexible and Multipurpose

Aurona allows to create various websites for complex and scalable projects.

SEO Friendly

Valid code and performance optimized framework make SEO easy and hassle-free.

Consistency is the Key

At Aurona, consistency is a key factor in web design for both visual elements and functionality. It also gives your users a positive experience.
